quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  3,195,"Nuko Nyagasani wabo abakirira ubusabe (agira ati) “Mu by’ukuri, njye sinagira imfabusa igikorwa cyakozwe n’umwe muri mwe, yaba uw’igitsina gabo cyangwa uw’igitsina gore, kuko mukomokanaho (murareshya mu guhemberwa ibyo mukora). Bityo ba bandi bimutse bakanameneshwa mu ngo zabo, bagatotezwa bazira kugana inzira yanjye, bakarwana, bakanicwa, rwose nzabababarira ibyaha byabo nanabinjize mu busitani (Ijuru) butembamo imigezi. Ibyo ni ibihembo biturutse kwa Allah, kandi kwa Allah ni ho hari ibihembo byiza.”"
  3,196,Ntuzashukwe n’umudendezo abahakanye bafite ku isi
  3,197,"Ni umunezero w’akanya gato, hanyuma ubuturo bwabo bukaba mu muriro wa Jahanamu kandi ni yo buturo bubi"
  3,198,"Ariko ba bandi batinye Nyagasani wabo, bazagororerwa ubusitani butembamo imigezi (mu ijuru), bazabubamo ubuziraherezo. Bizaba ari izimano rivuye kwa Allah, kandi ibiri kwa Allah ni akarusho ku bakora neza"
  3,199,"Mu by’ukuri mu bahawe ibitabo harimo abemera Allah n’ibyo mwahishuriwe (Qur’an) ndetse n’ibyo bahishuriwe (Tawurati n’Ivanjili); bibombarika imbere ya Allah. Ntibagurana amagambo ya Allah indonke (n’ubwo zaba) nke; abo bazahabwa ingororano zabo kwa Nyagasani wabo. Kandi mu by’ukuri, Allah ni Ubanguka mu ibarura"
  3,200,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimwihangane munihanganishanye, kandi mushikame (ku rugamba), ndetse mugandukire Allah kugira ngo mugere ku ntsinzi"